To build dde-linux2.6:
 - go to dde-linux2.6/pkg/dde/include/ddekit
 - create symlinks, which point to each of the DDEKit header files
 - go to dde-linux2.6 directory
 - run make O=/path/to/builddir config
 - configure build options
 - run make O=/path/to/builddir
 - libdde-linux26.a, libdde-linux26_net.a, libdde-linux26_block.a, and
   libdde-linux26_char.a are built

